Description: Saudi Airlines Catering Co (known as: Saudi Airlines Catering) is a public company, listed on Saudi Stock Exchange “Tadawul” (TDWL) since July 2012. Saudi Airlines Catering operates within the Commercial  and Professional Services sector focusing on Diversified Support Services. Saudi Airlines Catering is based in Jeddah, Saudi Arabia and was established in January 2008.
